sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Dashboard as "Railway Dashboard"
    participant Service as "falkordb Service"
    participant Proxy as "TCP Proxy"
    participant DNS as "External DNS"

    User->>Dashboard: Navigate to falkordb service
    User->>Dashboard: Settings → Networking
    User->>Dashboard: Click "Enable TCP Proxy"
    
    Dashboard->>Service: Configure proxy endpoint
    Service->>Proxy: Allocate public endpoint
    Proxy->>DNS: Register domain<br/>monorail.proxy.rlwy.net
    
    Dashboard->>User: Display endpoint<br/>RAILWAY_TCP_PROXY_DOMAIN<br/>RAILWAY_TCP_PROXY_PORT
    
    Note over User,DNS: TCP Proxy now forwards<br/>external traffic to internal service